{"tid":1301463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係，我好驚輸，但我更驚對佢地唔住","createTime":"2019-07-09T15:53:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T19:35:38.000Z","uid":45643,"like":166,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"7ad81209aeb700eb97f8b399addffb510b299c21","tid":1301463,"uid":45643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:53:03.000Z","msg":"後日，粱義士就出殯<br />\n已經有六位義士犧牲左，有超過60位巴絲比人拉左<br />\n佢地為左香港，可以命都唔要<br />\n<br />\n11月，就會係區議會選舉，今次會係打擊建制派票倉既好機會，只要我地係建制派手上拎得夠多區議會議席，就可以一步步推倒佢地既票倉，到時係立法會拎返屬於香港人既話事權。<br />\n<br />\n六位義士已經走左，但佢地既遺志，我地會堅守落去。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.upmedia.mg/upload/article/20190705112029513628.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upmedia.mg%2Fupload%2Farticle%2F20190705112029513628.jpg&h=0106383b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[2019區議會選舉]整合18區資料 睇下自己果區有冇人選 一齊重奪社區 ！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1291186/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1291186/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"f5927a09798c6f821f0bdfb168f827c0c08d78b4","tid":1301463,"uid":45643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:54:11.000Z","msg":"[招募] 參選助選觀塘區區議會<br />\ntg group:  <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/CwPIBkcxUtc5YO4TgbggRw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FCwPIBkcxUtc5YO4TgbggRw&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBK9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=8d6b91bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/CwPIBkcxUtc5YO4TgbggRw</a>"},{"pid":"07815937aa6b680191343ae59e75ff6fbc05f671","tid":1301463,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:54:56.000Z","msg":"<code>7.10前 - 一人一信反DQ - Link 1</code><br />\n<code>7.10 - 19:00~22:30 - 麥小姐追思會 ＠ 中環愛丁堡廣場</code><br />\n<code>7.11 - 梁烈士公眾告別禮 - Link 2</code><br />\n<code>7.11 -  油尖旺區議會夢遊 - Link 3</code><br />\n<code>7.13 - 15:30 - 光復上水 ＠ 上水花園第一號</code><br />\n<code>7.14 - 沙田區大遊行 - Link 4</code><br />\n<code>7.28 - 將軍澳遊行 - Link 5</code><br />\n<cod